projectGridLines.description:
Project 1

Title: Geospatial Data Insights

Description: Develop analytics and models on various Geospatial features and business features

Skill sets: Python, Machine Learning, Data Engineering, Data Science

Traits expectation: Passionate, Quick Learning, Problem Solving

Expected learning: Building Geospatial Models for Business Insights

Specific courses required for project execution: Machine Learning, Python, PyTorch

Project 2

Title: Usage Analytics

Description: Derive multiple KPIs for Product Usage Analytics from data

Skill sets: Python, Data Engineering, Data Science

Traits expectation: Passionate, Quick Learning, Problem Solving

Expected learning: Data Engineering Skills, Real time and batch processing, Analytics Backend Development

Specific courses required for project execution: Python, Data Engineering
